programme.desc: On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed.
programme.sub-title: A Night of Horror at Devil's Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case)

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Mysterious Disappearences in Paris - Christelle Leroy
programme.desc: On March 21th 1991, Pascale Escarfail, 19 years old, is discovered dead at her studio in the 14th arrondissement of Paris, she was raped then stabbed multiple times.
programme.sub-title: Mysterious Disappearences in Paris - Christelle Leroy

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Willy Pomonti Case
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Murdered For a Fake Treasure - Troadec Case
programme.desc: On March 28th 2013, the burnt body of Anne Barbot, 38 years old, is discovered in a forest of Maine-et-Loire.
programme.sub-title: Murdered For a Fake Treasure - Troadec Case

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Christophe Lejard Case
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. An execution, which at first glance doesn't square with the profile of a quiet family man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Laurence Dromard Case
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators don't understand who could want her dead.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Drost Notthoff Case
programme.desc: On September 11th 2011, in Èze, near Monaco, the owner of a luxury villa discovers the lifeless hanging body of his tenant, a rich German businessman.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: A Strange Hanging - Chantal Ternik Case
programme.desc: On April 3th 2003, Chantal Ternik, a 48 year old housewife, is discovered hanged in her house of Sanary-sur-Mer, in Var.
programme.sub-title: A Strange Hanging - Chantal Ternik Case

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Champion vs. Creator, Part 1
programme.desc: Yugi and friends enter the castle to discover Kaiba ready to duel Pegasus with Mokuba's soul hanging in the balance! The power of the Millennium Eye gives Pegasus the ability to read other people's minds.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Champion vs. Creator, Part 2
programme.desc: Kaiba is helpless against Pegasus's Toon World deck and mind-reading abilities. As the duel ends, Pegasus imprisons Kaiba's soul into a card, just like Grandpa and Mokuba!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Night Before
programme.desc: Yugi vows to overthrow Pegasus for the sake of his Grandpa. Tristan leads an exploration party to uncover Pegasus's secrets. While Joey sleeps, Bandit Keith steals from him the card that permits his entry in the final battle!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Duel Identity Part, 1
programme.desc: Under Pegasus's glare, Yugi is distracted from his duel with Mai. After making foolish errors and allowing Mai to gain a huge advantage with her Harpie's Pet Dragon, will Yugi gather his focus or succumb to the pressure?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Duel Identity Part, 2
programme.desc: Mai has rebounded from her previous loss to Joey to become a better duelist. Has Yugi learned from his loss to Kaiba, or is the emotional defeat still weighing on his heart? The answer is in the cards!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Keith's Machinations, Part 1
programme.desc: Joey searches for the card that permits him to enter the final battle, not realizing Bandit Keith has stolen it. As he struggles to accept the fact that Serenity will be blind forever, he receives help from a new friend!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Keith's Machinations, Part 2
programme.desc: After Bandit Keith's Machine deck forces Joey to take the defensive, Joey mimics Keith's battle strategy to metalize his Red-Eyes Black Dragon! Is victory assured, or does the cheater Bandit Keith literally have one last card up his sleeve?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Best of Friends Best of Duelists, Part 1
programme.desc: Joey challenges Yugi for the right to face Pegasus. In a battle between friends, a fierce match ensues between the two people who know each other's strategies and cards.
programme.sub-title: Best of Friends Best of Duelists, Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Best of Friends Best of Duelists, Part 2
programme.desc: Yugi is shocked as Joey uses the Time Wizard card on him. It's the very same card Yugi gave Joey as a sign of friendship!
programme.sub-title: Best of Friends Best of Duelists, Part 2

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 1
programme.desc: Yugi prepares for the ultimate battle against Pegasus with the souls of Grandpa, Kaiba, and Mokuba on the line.
programme.sub-title: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 2
programme.desc: Pegasus punishes Yugi using the same Toon Deck and mind-reading abilities he used on Kaiba. As Pegasus turns Yugi's monsters against him, Yugi loses the will to battle. Will Pegasus capture Yugi's soul into a card, just like Kaiba?
programme.sub-title: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 2

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 3
programme.desc: Yugi has found a counter to Pegasus's mind-reading ability: Yugi switches back and forth between his two souls! Yugi is able to destroy Pegasus's Toon World, but the duel has just only begun. The next level of the deadly Shadow Game is about to start!
programme.sub-title: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 3

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 4
programme.desc: Yugi crumples under the power of the Shadow Game. His friends yell desperate encouragement, but their voices cannot penetrate the sphere of darkness. Yugi's chance at victory is slipping away, as is his life!
programme.sub-title: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 4

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 5
programme.desc: Pegasus summons Relinquished, a fearsome monster that can consume Yugi's Duel Monsters! Yugi counters with… Kuriboh?
programme.sub-title: Yugi vs. Pegasus Match of the Millennium, Part 5

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Aftermath
programme.desc: Yugi meets a mysterious Egyptian named Shadi who enters Yugi's mind with the Millennium Key. What are these Millennium Items, and do they hold the answer to the mystery behind the Shadow Games?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Wrath of Rebecca
programme.desc: Yugi and friends return from the Duelist Kingdom only to meet a young girl named Rebecca who demands that Grandpa return Blue-Eyes White Dragon to her.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Ties of Friendship
programme.desc: Rebecca mistakenly believes that Grandpa stole the Blue-Eyes White Dragon from her grandfather. Yugi must defend the Blue-Eyes White Dragon to teach her that it's not the power of the cards, but the heart that's in them that counts.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Ledgendary Heroes, Part 1
programme.desc: The two-faced Board of Directors of Kaiba Corporation trap Kaiba inside a virtual reality game. Mokuba recruits Yugi and Joey to free Kaiba from this ultimate game where losing equals death!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Ledgendary Heroes, Part 2
programme.desc: The quest for Kaiba continues with a little help from… Mai? But can YUGI and friends adapt to a virtual world where the rules and strategies keep changing every step of the way?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Ledgendary Heroes, Part 3
programme.desc: Yugi and friends rescue Kaiba, but they are still stuck in the game! The only exit is past a Five-Headed Dragon, but in the difficult duel, Joey, Mokuba, and Mailose all their life points!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Dungeon Dice Monsters, Part 1
programme.desc: Duke Devlin defeats Joey and humiliates him in public, forcing Yugi to challenge Duke to a duel. However, this will not be a Duel Monsters duel, but a new game named Dungeon Dice Monsters!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Dungeon Dice Monsters, Part 2
programme.desc: In exchange for Joey's freedom, Yugi agrees to give up Duel Monsters forever if he loses. Unfamiliar with the rules, Yugi gets off to a rough start.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Dungeon Dice Monsters, Part 3
programme.desc: Yugi uses his innate gaming skills to turn the tables on Duke, but Duke has one more rule to mention: All creatures take up territory on the grid-like board. With no room to summon any new monsters, Yugi's position is helpless!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Dungeon Dice Monsters, Part 4
programme.desc: After Duke's all-powerful Orogoth The Relentless dices Yugi's entire cadre of monsters into shreds, Yugi only has one turn left before he loses all his heart points!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Mystery Duelist Part 1
programme.desc: An arcane fortune teller steals the Millennium Puzzle and Yugi must defeat him in a duel to win it back.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Mystery Duelist Part 2
programme.desc: The mysterious menace controlling Bandit Keith shatters the Millennium Puzzle into pieces before setting the dueling arena ablaze. Can Yugi put the Millennium Puzzle back together and save the spirit before the entire room is engulfed in flames?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Past is Present
programme.desc: The origin of Duel Monsters is revealed. Using the magic of the Millennium Necklace, Egyptian historian Ishizu Ishtar shows Kaiba how Duel Monsters was played millenniums ago.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Steppin' Out
programme.desc: The spirit of the Millennium Puzzle realizes that his memories of ancient Egypt have faded, but Tea helps him uncover the mysteries of his past.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Obelisk The Tormentor
programme.desc: Yugi learns that he was a powerful Pharaoh who saved the world five thousand years ago, and he must now save the world again.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Stalked By the Rare Hunters
programme.desc: Joey is cornered by a group of sinister Rare Hunters who force Joey into a duel. If he loses, the Rare Hunters get his precious Red-Eyes Black Dragon!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Yugi Vs. Rare Hunter Part 1 - Battle City Begins
programme.desc: It's time to master new rules and monsters; let the Battle City Tournament commence! In the first duel of the tournament, Yugi challenges the Rare Hunter to win back Joey's Red-Eyes Black Dragon.
programme.sub-title: Yugi Vs. Rare Hunter Part 1 - Battle City Begins

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Yugi Vs. Rare Hunter Part 2 - Up Against Exodia
programme.desc: Yugi figures out the Rare Hunter's strategy to summon the almighty Exodia, but it's too late to stop him. The Rare Hunter already has four pieces of Exodia in his hand, and the fifth and final piece is on top of his deck.
programme.sub-title: Yugi Vs. Rare Hunter Part 2 - Up Against Exodia

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The ESP Duelist Part 1
programme.desc: The psychic duelist Espa Roba defeats Rex Raptor as easy as a chumpasaurus, and Joey's next on his hit list. What chance does Joey have when Espa Roba has the telepathic ability to read all the cards in Joey's hand?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The ESP Duelist Part 2
programme.desc: Joey discovers that Espa Roba's extrasensory perception was a hoax, that he's not yet free from Espa's mental manipulations.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Master of Magicians Part 1
programme.desc: The magician duelist Arkana transports Yugi to the world's most lethal dueling arena where the loser gets sent to the Shadow Realm. Yugi must win this duel or he'll lose much more than his Dark Magician.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Master of Magicians Part 2
programme.desc: It's Dark Magician versus Dark Magician! However, while Yugi only controls one Dark Magician, Arkana has three residing in his deck. Though outnumbered, Yugi will never give up as long as he believes in the heart of the cards.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Master of Magicians Part 3
programme.desc: To counter Arkana's Dark Magician, Yugi pulls a rabbit out of his hat: the Dark Magician Girl!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Playing with a Parasite Part 1
programme.desc: The trickster Weevil Underwood spins a web of lies to bait Joey into a lopsided duel.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Playing with a Parasite Part 2
programme.desc: Joey swats Perfectly Ultimate Great Moth only to have Weevil let loose the ferocious Insect Queen, the crown jewel of insects that grows in strength for every creepy crawler it cannibalizes. Will Weevil's royal ravager swarm Joey into submission?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Mime Control Part 1
programme.desc: Yugi faces off against another of Marik's nefarious Rare Hunters, the silent but deadly Strings.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 301
programme.desc: I dag møter vi bl.a. Jane, som ikke lenger har lyst på sex på grunn av de stygge brystene sine, og Julie, som misliker seg selv på grunn av de store arrene hun fikk etter en brystreduksjon.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 904
programme.desc: Jeannes bryster hindrer henne i å leve et normalt liv. Gitte skammer seg over beina og bruker enormt mye tid og energi på å skjule dem.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 308
programme.desc: Lizette sitter igjen med et knallhardt bryst etter en forstørrende operasjon, mens Diana går med voldsomme smerter etter en brystreduksjon. Begge håper de å få hjelp av de erfarne kirurgene.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 503
programme.desc: Under sin siste fødsel gjennomgikk Sonja et akutt keisersnitt som, noe utradisjonelt, ble kuttet vertikalt på Sonjas mage. Sonjas navle ble kuttet opp, og resultatet er til en stor ulempe for henne.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 309
programme.desc: Ditte har brukt 120 000 kroner på å få større bryster - som er asymmetriske. Eva har fått utført en brystreduksjon, men føler seg nå mer maskulin enn feminin.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 802
programme.desc: For første gang i programmets historie har både mor og datter havnet i et plastisk mareritt, og begge trenger hjelp.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 302
programme.desc: I dagens episode møter vi bl.a. Isabella, som fikk utført brystforstørring som 18-åring for å ligne Pamela Anderson, men som i dag sitter igjen med to steinharde kuler på brystkassen.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 104
programme.desc: Pernille får kick av å få utført plastisk kirurgi, men armene hennes er vansiret av store arr. Mille drømmer om at de feilopererte brystene hennes blir fiksa før bryllupet.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 205
programme.desc: I denne episoden møter vi bl.a. Dianne, som fikk fjernet brystene grunnet mistanke om kreft, men som nå lever alene fordi hun føler seg utilpass, og Anette, som fikk foretatt en hudoperasjon i utlandet.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 303
programme.desc: Doris var med i en alvorlig bussulykke og i dag sliter hun med ekstreme bivirkninger av en operasjon som egentlig skulle ha reddet utseendet hennes etter ulykken.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 601
programme.desc: Charlotte fikk fjernet brystimplantatene sine på grunn av komplikasjoner. Etter det fikk hun en protese for å kompensere for størrelsen på brystene, men protesen er både ubehagelig og upraktisk.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 106
programme.desc: Vi møter fire personer som har gjort plastikkirugi som har fått ødeleggende konsekvenser: blant annet Lone som lever i frykt for at implantatene hennes er kreftfremkallende.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 305
programme.desc: I dag møter vi bl.a. Jonna, som føler at magen hennes ligner et bombekrater etter en operasjon, og Christina, som har tre mislykkede operasjoner bak seg.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 703
programme.desc: Den tidligere burlesk-danseren Grethe måtte i 2011 fjerne begge brystene som en del av hennes behandling av brystkreft.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 101
programme.desc: I kveldens episode møter vi fire ofre for plastiskkirurgiske feiloperasjoner.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 501
programme.desc: Siden puberteten, har Tascha vært lei av sine asymmetriske bryster og har hatt en brystoperasjon. Men Tascha fikk ikke symmetrien hun drømte om, og i dag skammer hun seg over brystene.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 805
programme.desc: Som tenåring har Linette en skjev skillevegg i nesen som gir henne pustevansker. Som 21-åring får hun derfor tilbud om en neseoperasjon for å fikse problemet, men ender opp med en skjev nese.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 105
programme.desc: Sabine fant et tilbud på nettet, men måtte betale dyrt for å spare 50 prosent.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 608
programme.desc: I 2011 velger Sabina å ta en brystforstørrelsesoperasjon. Men allerede et par dager etter operasjonen oppdager hun at brystene hennes henger.

programme.title: Skjønnhetsfellen Danmark: Episode 202
programme.desc: I dagens episode møter vi bl.a. Pernille, som føler seg fanget i sitt eget hjem, og Linda, som er så hemmet av et arr på magen at hun møter opp tidlig på jobb for å unngå å skifte med andre.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: New Girl In Town
programme.desc: Geordie-gjengen er tilbake og skaper hollabaloy! Chloe blir en slem heks for å få ha seg med Scott. Holly har en diger hemmelighet, men kan hun fortelle den? Og en ny deltager sjokkerer og får liv i gutta, men gjør Chloe svært stressa.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Hello Single Charlotte!
programme.desc: Charlotte kommer med store nyheter for Gaz . Kan Holly avsløre hemmeligheten sin nå? Aaron og Scotts dater med den nye jenta Chantelle ender dårlig.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Holly's Tears
programme.desc: Charlotte pusser snoppdetektivene på Gaz, og Scott forbløffer alle da han vil være kjæreste med den nye jenta Chantelle. Holly krangler med Charlotte da hun ser henne kysse Chloe.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Girls Just Want To Have Fun
programme.desc: Mens Holly er borte tar Chloe og Charlotte vennskapet sitt til neste nivå. Chantelles plan for å teste Scott går helt feil og Chloe er rask til å utnytte det. Charlotte forsøker å ordne opp i ting med Holly.
programme.sub-title: Girls Just Want To Have Fun

programme.title: Geordie Shore: You're The Victim!
programme.desc: Sjefen Anna spanderer en tur til Hull på Geordiene. Gaz og Charlotte tilbringer natten sammen, og Chloe forteller endelig Chantelle sannheten om hva hun ga Scott. I tillegg kommer det enda en overraskelse når Marnie vender tilbake.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: The 'L' Bomb
programme.desc: Festaften! En ny gutt ankommer og Chloe gleder seg. Charlotte sjekker opp en fyr rett foran Gaz. Marnie blir gal når en av Aarons venninner dukker opp. Den nye gutten fyrer opp krangelen mellom Scott og Chantelle.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Breaking Girl Code
programme.desc: Nest siste episode. Marnie kliner med den nye gutten Marty for å gi Aaron en lærepenge. Charlotte støtter Chloe når det tar helt av mellom jentene. Gary og Charlotte ender opp i sengehalmen og ryster hele Geordie-huset.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: More Than Friends
programme.desc: Det er siste episode og Geordie-gjengen skuffer ikke. Gary kommer tilbake og slipper en bombe. Den nye typen Marty får ikke stå med Chloe. Scott og Chantelle blir 'venner'. Holly må ta et viktig valg og avslutningen kommer som et sjokk!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Gaz's Shock Revelation
programme.desc: Geordies er tilbake! Big Boss Anna har sendt gjengen til Magaluf. Marnie ønsker mer av Aaron, det svirrer et stygt rykte om Holly, og Marty åpner seg for Chloe. Ting ser bra ut helt til Chloe blir sjalu og det hele sparkes i gang.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: The G-Bomb
programme.desc: Ibiza. På båtfesten er single Gaz tilbake og klarer å sjekke opp Chantelle. Men hvordan vil Holly reagere når hun får vite det? Chloe klekker ut en plan for å få Marty, men han flykter ut av et vindu.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Broken Relationships
programme.desc: Maga. Big Boss Anna er rasende når gjengen endelig returnerer fra Ibiza. Marnies plan om å få Aarons oppmerksomhet slår feil og parforholdet er i krise når Nathan blir involvert. Gaz og Holly prøver å snake ut om Chantelle-kysset.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Gary And Sophie's Showdown
programme.desc: Kavos. Chloe blir sjalu på Holly og Marty, Marnie er opprørt over at Aaron dro uten å snakke med henne først, og Scott mottar noen store nyheter. En sjokkerende ankomst får store konsekvenser for Gaz og Chantelle.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Here's Nathan!
programme.desc: Kavos. Det er pinlig stemning mellom Sophie, Gaz og Chantelle etter krangelen deres. Aaron er endelig tilbake, men Marnie er ikke fornøyd. Chantelle og Marty kjemper om Chloe, noe som fører til at Chantelle tar en stor avgjørelse.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Playing Mind Games
programme.desc: Dagen etter at Chantelle dro, så får Sophie store nyheter fra sjefen Anna, Aaron må hentes av ambulanse, og Chloe forsøker å komme seg over Marty. Men når Marty sjekker opp noen, går festen fort nedover.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Gaz's True Feelings

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Hole In One
programme.desc: Geordiene når bristepunktet. Marty prøver å gjøre det godt igjen, men vil Chloe tilgi ham? Vil Aaron og Marnie klare å finne tilbake til hverandre? På bassengfesten har Holly problemer med å holde seg på beina, og Kyles stunt slår feil.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: The Big Decision
programme.desc: Chloe og Marty flørter igjen. Klarer de å bare være gode venner? Sjefen Anna har store nyheter til Kyle. Holly misliker det og bestemmer seg for noe som vil forandre alt for familien. Sesongslutt.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: New Workers

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Big Decisions
programme.desc: Annas plan for å finne de beste nykommerne fortsetter. Aaron og Marty bestemmer seg for å bli bedre kjent med Sarah og Abbie. Etter krangelen med Zahida får Chloe store nyheter, og familjen blir sjokkert når to nye deltagere kommer.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Testing The Newbies
programme.desc: Nathan vil teste hvor ville de nye arbeiderne er. Chloe vender tilbake, Marnie og Marty barker sammen over Aaron og alle får et kjempesjokk når de ser den seneste nykommeren. Marty prøver å snakke med Chloe, som vender ham ryggen.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Toxic Shots Syndrome

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Merp Walk

programme.title: Delete Me: Rising to Fame

programme.desc: Marion og Marit - bestevenner med store drømmer. Marion ønsker desperat å være en del av den populære gjengen, mens Marit kun tenker på Miami. Hva som skjedde ved bassenget blir endelig avslørt.

programme.title: Gutter: Hjemsøkte netter
programme.desc: Leonora sliter med å sove etter Lasses død. Robin drar ut for å feste med korguttene, men når en tilfeldig jente forlater klubben etter å ha sett Nikolaj, er han ivrig etter å finne ut hva hun var redd for.

programme.title: Gutter: Tid for bekjennelse
programme.desc: Leonora og Robin prøver å finne ut mer om jenta fra nattklubben, og bestemmer seg for å infiltrere en Halloween-fest. Tilbake i fortiden oppdager Nikolaj og Lasse et nytt aspekt ved forholdet deres.

programme.title: Gutter: Ritualet
programme.desc: Robin er fast bestemt på å finne ut hva som skjedde med Lasse, og han begynner sitt innvielsesritual i guttekoret. Mikael oppdager at Nikolaj og Emily har holdt en hemmelighet for ham.

programme.title: Gutter: Splittelse
programme.desc: Leonora bekymrer seg for at Robin kommer for nær Nikolaj og korguttene, noe som fører til en forstyrrelse i samarbeidet deres. I mellomtiden avslører Seb noen ødeleggende bevis om Robin til Nikolaj.

programme.title: Gutter: November Rave
programme.desc: Korguttene og hockeyjentene deltar begge på November Rave på øya, der Leonora bestemmer seg for å konfrontere Nikolaj om Lasses død. I mellomtiden møter Robin et kjent ansikt.

programme.title: Gutter: Tilgivelse
programme.desc: Nikolaj avslører sannheten om hva som egentlig skjedde ved sjøen sammen med Ingrid og Lasse. Robin tar en drastisk livsavgjørelse, og Nikolaj blir tvunget til å konfrontere Mikael om handlingene hans.

programme.title: Ida tar ansvar: How To Respond in an Active Shooter Situation
programme.desc: Ida flytter hjemmefra for å studere psykologi på Blindern. Hun er redd for det meste, men hennes største frykt er terror. Det blir ikke bedre når hun møter Aksel, som tilbringer mye tid på incel-fora på nettet.
programme.sub-title: How To Respond in an Active Shooter Situation

programme.title: Ida tar ansvar: Noen burde bare ligge med dem
programme.desc: Ida blir sjarmert av sykkelbudet Jonas, mens hun prøver å finne sin plass på Blindern. Aksel kontakter henne for å få hjelp med eksamen, og Ida blir introdusert for ideen om å ligge med incels for å forhindre terror.
programme.sub-title: Noen burde bare ligge med dem

programme.desc: I et forsøk på å unngå Aksel rømmer Ida til sin far på Sørlandet. Når hun ankommer viser det seg at det er mye Idas far ikke har fortalt henne om livet sitt.

programme.title: Ida tar ansvar: Let the Reaping Begin
programme.desc: Aksel begynner å oppføre seg annerledes, og kutter brått kontakten med Ida. Siri fra studiet har blitt singel og er på jakt etter en rebound, dette gir Ida en Idé som potensielt kan gagne både Aksel og Siri.

programme.title: Ida tar ansvar: Bare to uker til
programme.desc: Idas fatale feiltrinn med Aksel skaper store problemer for henne og hun prøver å holde frykten på avstand ved å distrahere seg med Jonas. Men Aksel har ikke tenkt å la henne slippe unna så lett.

programme.title: Ida tar ansvar: Survival of the Fittest
programme.desc: Presset på Ida øker og Aksels påvirkning på livet hennes er i ferd med å ødelegge relasjonen til Jonas. Ida oppsøker sin mor for å kanskje kunne få noen råd, men moren viser seg å være en dårlig støtte.

programme.desc: Aksel forbereder seg på dagen som kan forandre hans liv. Samtidig etterforsker to politibetjenter en voldssak mot en uidentifisert ung kvinne, og sporene leder dem til Idas studentbolig.

programme.title: Ida tar ansvar: Frykten er stort sett irrasjonell
programme.desc: Ida prøver desperat å komme i kontakt med Aksel og oppsøker moren hans i et forsøk på å finne ham. Ida må til slutt ta et viktig valg, har hun tenkt å la frykten eller fornuften vinne?

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 408
programme.desc: Mattias kjører over 100 kviger og okser til beite. Tove laster tømmer i skogene i Småland. Jörgen kjører en transformator, men alt fungerer ikke som det skal!

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 501
programme.desc: Jörgen kjører en 50 tonns transformator i Skåne – men problemene avløser hverandre. Mattias har reist til den finske grensen for å frakte alpakkaer. Emina leverer fisk i Skåne.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 502
programme.desc: Pappa Roine og Mattias laster høyballer – men plutselig stopper hjullasteren. Linda leverer drinker rundt i Stockholm – og benytter anledningen til å besøke forloveden Magnus. Piraten legger asfalt.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 503
programme.desc: Biltransportøren Robin må være ekstra forsiktig når han skal frakte en dyr Lincoln på lasteplanet! Det samme gjelder Micke som skal kjøre et dyrt spabad til Uddevalla.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 504
programme.desc: Tove kjører tømmer i Småland – og møter fans midt i skogen. Slamsugeren Magnus skal tømme et basseng på et renseanlegg. Kranfører Amanda er på et vindkraftverk på Gotland – men risikerer å miste båten.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 505
programme.desc: Elin sparker dagen i gang i Stockholm med komplisert lossing og tidspress. Tim kjører etsende last – og han må derfor være ekstra forsiktig på veiene. Peo sliter med containerne sine i Åre.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 506
programme.desc: Vi følger yrkessjåførene som jobber døgnet rundt for å levere forskjellige typer av varer over hele landet - og for å utføre viktige samfunnstiltak som holder Sverige i gang, fra nord til sør.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 507
programme.desc: Vi følger yrkessjåførene som jobber døgnet rundt for å levere forskjellige typer av varer over hele landet - og for å utføre viktige samfunnstiltak som holder Sverige i gang, fra nord til sør.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 508
programme.desc: Johannes skal levere brakker – men kaster ved et uhell nøklene på taket. Spesialtransportørene og ekteparet Anton og Angelica har en kjøretur sammen - til Norge. Emina kjører kjøtt i Skåne.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 701
programme.desc: I det nordlige vinterlandskapet må Anton stoppe transporten av et tungt toglokomotiv når tilhengeren går i stykker. Elin, en melkebilsjåfør, starter dagen rolig, helt til en melkeslange ryker og kaos oppstår.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 702
programme.desc: For Denkan fra Göteborg blir transporten et mareritt. Etter å ha reparert en lekk bremseklokke blinker lysene rødt. Bremsene overopphetes, og han må skynde seg dit med et brannslukningsapparat.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 703
programme.desc: Kellys stressende dag blir verre når det viser seg at flere bedrifter holder stengt på grunn av ferien. Emina må rekke en fotballkamp, men det blir full stopp hos den første kunden da hun ikke kommer seg inn på lageret.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 704
programme.desc: Når Roine laster okser, nekter de å gå opp på lastebilen. Og det er ikke lett å få okser på 1100 kg til å adlyde. Emina leverer fisk i sommervarmen, men havner bak saktegående feriegjester.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 705
programme.desc: Tove dekker opp for vikarer som har sommerferie og jobber derfor på dagtid. De nye arbeidstidene i det sommerlige Småland byr på andre problemer enn vanlig.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 706
programme.desc: Kranfører Carl har blitt bedt om å flytte en havnekran som veier nesten 200 tonn og er 33 meter høy. Men arbeidet må brått avbrytes fordi det er fare for at kranen kan velte når en del mangler.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 707
programme.desc: Mattias må hente kviger i Enköping og deretter hente en okse på Ljusterö, noe som ikke viser seg å være lett.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 708
programme.desc: I Stockholm har Max en tøff dag og sliter med å få med seg alle søppeldunkene som skal tømmes. Han gleder seg til den siste tømmingen for dagen.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 201
programme.desc: Simon fra Piteå har tatt over som administrerende direktør i transportfirmaet etter sin far Erik. Jörgen fra Höganäs må kjøre et 58 meter langt blad til en vindturbin og støter på utfordringer i svingene.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 202
programme.desc: Erik Lundman i Lundmans transportfirma sliter med en kloakktank, postbud Stephanie gjør en feil og taper tid under en hastetur, og spesialtransportør Jari får utrolig nok tre punkteringer.

programme.title: Svenske Truckers: Episode 203
programme.desc: Jesper er bekymret for å komme for sent til avlastningen i Danmark. Tove får en dårlig start på dagen og krasjer med tømmerbilen sin. Og Jari havner i feil havn under lossing.

programme.title: Survivor: We Got a Rat
programme.desc: Just days into the game, castaways drop their buffs and switch from two to three tribes. Also, a castaway's future in the game is in jeopardy when they're caught sending a message to another tribe.

programme.title: Survivor: What's the Beef?
programme.desc: Three castaways leave it all on the beach in a gut-wrenching challenge, and two castaways plead for their lives in the game at a heated tribal council. Also, Abi-Maria continues to ruffle feathers with her tribe.

programme.title: Survivor: A Snake in the Grass
programme.desc: One castaway embraces a new, more personal style of play for his second chance. Also, one castaway risks ruining a good thing by going against her own alliance.

programme.title: Survivor: Bunking with the Devil
programme.desc: One castaway is pulled from the game due to a family emergency. Also, Tribes drop their buffs and switch it up for the second time, and castaways chow down on local delicacies in a classic immunity challenge.

programme.title: Survivor: Play to Win
programme.desc: Thirteen shocked castaways come together for the largest merge ever. Also, history repeats itself for two feuding castaways, and the season's first individual immunity challenge is a classic game of balance.

programme.title: Survivor: You Call, We'll Haul
programme.desc: An intense water challenge leaves castaways thirsty for a much-needed reward. Also, immunity hangs in the balance as castaways attempt to steady themselves, and a shocking tribal council takes an unexpected turn.

programme.title: Survivor: Witches Coven
programme.desc: One castaway risks their safety in the game in order to gain an advantage. Also, another castaway steps up in a brutal individual immunity challenge to further their game, and three castaways deemed the "Witches Coven" stir the pot at camp.

programme.title: Survivor: Like Selling Your Soul to the Devil
programme.desc: Castaways' spirits are drowning in a relentless rain storm, but a fun challenge reward offers a few players a glimpse into the Cambodian culture. Also, the "voting block" strategy used this season continues to keep Castaways on their toes.
programme.sub-title: Like Selling Your Soul to the Devil

programme.title: Survivor: My Wheels Are Spinning
programme.desc: Castaways' spirits are drowning in a relentless rain storm, but a fun challenge reward offers a few players a glimpse into the Cambodian culture. Also, the "voting block" strategy used this season continues to keep Castaways on their toes.

programme.title: Survivor: Tiny Little Shanks to the Heart
programme.desc: Emotions run deep when loved ones visit the island, and a desperate reward challenge leaves castaways' heads spinning. Also, exhaustion takes a serious toll on one castaway in the middle of an immunity battle.
programme.sub-title: Tiny Little Shanks to the Heart

programme.title: Survivor: Villains Have More Fun
programme.desc: The castaways scramble to solidify a plan for the final three. Also, a frightening incident at the immunity challenge sends shockwaves through the entire tribe, and castaways are rewarded with a spiritual recharge at the temples of Cambodia.

programme.title: Survivor: Lie, Cheat and Steal
programme.desc: Six castaways battle it out for a shot in the final three, and a shocking tribal council delivers a Survivor first. Later, the final three castaways plead their cases for the $1 million prize, on the two-hour season finale.

programme.title: Survivor: Live Reunion Show
programme.desc: The castaways reunite in Los Angeles to discuss the season. Jeff Probst hosts.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model
programme.desc: A hi-tech runway analyzes the girls’ strut & Tyra, Miss J and Jay Manuel assess which 14 show the most Top Model potential.
programme.sub-title: The Notorious Fierce Fourteen-Top Model Inauguration

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: The Ladder Of Model Success
programme.desc: Benny Ninja is back to educate the girls about posing, but one of the girls takes contorting her body a little too far.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: You’re Beautiful, Now Change
programme.desc: The ladies are excited when Tyra reveals it’s time for makeovers. Hair is cut and tears are shed when the girls see their new looks for the first time.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Fierce Eyes
programme.desc: The ladies practice their strut down a catwalk while wearing blindfolds and one girl shocks the judges when she decides to lift her dress while posing.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Natural Beauty
programme.desc: The contestants are thrilled when Paulina shows up to show them how to model unflattering clothing with style.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: The Fierce Awards
programme.desc: Tyra surprises the remaining girls with a one-on-one photoshoot to teach each girl how to find their most flattering pose.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Top Model Confidential
programme.desc: A look at never-before-seen footage of the cycle 11 contestants that includes the ladies improvising a rap in the hot tub, one girl revealing a hidden talent and a very candid chat between Tyra and the model wannabes.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Now You See Me, Now You Don’t
programme.desc: The ladies pull a disappearing act for this week’s challenge.
programme.sub-title: Now You See Me, Now You Don’t

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Planes, Trains and Slow Automobiles
programme.desc: The ladies pack their bags and head overseas to their European destination.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: The Final Five
programme.desc: The remaining five girls travel around town by boat for their go sees.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Good Times & Windmills
programme.desc: Paulina offers the girls advice on how to successfully model with a variety of items, including fish and toilet paper.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: America’s Next Top Model Is…
programme.desc: In the cycle 11 finale, the three finalists put their Top Model experience to the test when they shoot their final CoverGirl commercial & print ad.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: What Happens In Vegas + Fun And Games (Episodes 1 & 2)
programme.desc: Thirty-four finalists travel to Caesar’s Palace in Las Vegas where they being their inner-goddess to the surface for their very first photoshoot.
programme.sub-title: What Happens In Vegas + Fun And Games (Episodes 1 & 2)

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Do You Light The Way You Look?
programme.desc: The girls head to Bergdorff’s in New York City for makeovers! After receiving their new looks, the girls do their first photo session with Nigel Barker and must light themselves up.
programme.sub-title: Do You Light The Way You Look?

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: New York’s Finest
programme.desc: The girls learn runway etiquette with Miss J and walk the runway in a Jill Stuart fashion show. Two previous Top Model contestants surprise the girls and offer runway advice.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Put Your Best Face Forward
programme.desc: Cycle three contestant and model Tocarra drops by to host a slumber party & teaches the girls some helpful hints for a career in the modeling business.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Here’s Your Test
programme.desc: The house is divided and confrontational after last week’s shocking admission from one girl at the elimination panel.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Acting Like A Model
programme.desc: The girls are surprised to learn they will be working opposite Clay Aiken during an acting challenge. Cycle 11 winner, McKey, stops by to offer support while the girls prepare for their CoverGirl commercial.

programme.title: America's Next Top Model: Cycle 12 Rewind
programme.desc: Catch up with the cycle 12 girls in this look back at never-before-seen footage. Brand new moments full of tears, laughter and some catfights.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Revive Our Football!
programme.desc: Raimon uses Aitor and Gabi's stellar tandem skills to combat Lunar Sea's tactical play. When Arion uses his Fighting Spirit to even the score, momentum shifts to Raimon.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: He’s back!
programme.desc: Following in Aitor's footsteps, a new player tries out for Raimon. Coaches Evans and Sharp see his love for the game and readily accept him, and despite having only two months experience, he quickly integrates himself with the team.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Adversarial White Devil
programme.desc: Alpine has fallen under the control of Fifth Sector, and Raimon is tasked with rescuing them. Knowing that Alpine's stout defence can stand up against Thunderbolt, Raimon prepares a surprising new tactical play.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Fierce Fight on the Ice vs Alpine Jr High!
programme.desc: Alpine striker Njord Snio's special shot gives the team an early lead. While Raimon has mastered using spikes to run across the icy pitch, their new tactical play is powerless against Alpine's masterful skills.
programme.sub-title: Fierce Fight on the Ice vs Alpine Jr High!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Coach Sharp’s Apprehension!
programme.desc: After their ferocious match against Alpine, Coach Evans makes an announcement that rocks Arion and the rest of Raimon. Soon thereafter, the team starts a new training regimen that prevents them from touching the ball.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Challenge Against Kirkwood!
programme.desc: Raimon finds their core skills improving thanks to their coach's new training scheme. But while the team is committed to making their revolution happen, Arion and J.P. face trouble with a new special move.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Tactical confrontation! Love vs Sharp!
programme.desc: As the match begins, the stadium's unique gimmick proves an unexpected obstacle for both teams. The Kirkwood side, however, is united under their coach's words: "If we beat Raimon, we can see the road ahead."

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Arrival of Brave Samurai Musashi
programme.desc: As the second half begins, Roma manages to even the score. And while Raimon starts to find its flow, Langford Ash's selfish play threatens to rip Kirkwood apart.
programme.sub-title: The Arrival of Brave Samurai Musashi

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Miracle of the Revolutionary Wind
programme.desc: After a pitched battle against Kirkwood, Arion and the rest of Raimon train for their next match. The team undergoes a trial-and-error process with J.P., who is attempting to gain a Fighting Spirit in order to better contribute.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: A Mysterious Enemy. Mirage Middle School.
programme.desc: Raimon's quarterfinal opponent in Holy Road is Mirage Middle School, but while the team trains for the match, Wan-Chang's heart isn't in it. He's troubled both by his previous lineup demotion and Mirage striker Harrold Houdini.
programme.sub-title: A Mysterious Enemy. Mirage Middle School.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Impossible to Defend. Phantom Shot
programme.desc: The Mirage challenge begins with Wan-Chang in the starting line-up, and he sees the match as a chance to tell Harrold how he feels. Luke, meanwhile, is unable to give Wan-Chang the news he learned from the mysterious girl.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Shocking Baton Pass. Keeper Change.
programme.desc: Coach Sharp realizes how to take advantage of the stadium, and his new tactics give Raimon a quick second-half equalizer. Meanwhile, Wan-Chang finally learns the truth of his past from a primary-school friend.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Reunion of Fate
programme.desc: Raimon has finally advanced to the Holy Road semi-finals. Their next opponent, Universal Middle School, is said to have "perfect players" gifted in all aspects of football.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Glasswork Genius
programme.desc: Arion sets aside his anxiety, rekindles his passion for football, and devotes himself to practice once more. Meanwhile, Sam invites J.P. to try goalkeeping after seeing his performance on the pitch.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Sun Spirit Unleashed
programme.desc: The day of the Holy Road semi-final is here! Raimon, confident in their quest to restore "real" football, takes on the "perfect" Universal Middle School. But Arion sees a familiar face on the opposing sideline.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Arion versus Sol
programme.desc: Victor has shocking words for Arion: "You're the only one on Raimon who isn't playing seriously right now." Arion wonders if it's because of his concern for Sol Daystar, whose illness makes him too weak to withstand the rigors of the game.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Arion, the New Captain
programme.desc: The match against Universal is over, and Riccardo, who fell during the game, is undergoing emergency surgery. This puts the team captain out for the upcoming Holy Road championship, a major blow to Raimon's hopes.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Showdown in Zenith Stadium
programme.desc: A battered Victor tells a surprised Arion they must learn a certain special move if they hope to win. As Arion guides Raimon as captain, he secretly engages in a series of gruelling practices right up to the night before the championship.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Dragon Link, the Ultimate Foe
programme.desc: The Holy Road championship, the match that decides who becomes the next Holy Emperor, is finally here! An evenly fought first half ends with Fifth Sector's strongest and the freedom fighters of Raimon tied--a development that pleases Raimon to no end.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Final Holy War
programme.desc: The second half begins with all of Mount Olympus' players substituted out. Gyan Cinquedea, creator of Fifth Sector, serves as coach, and Raimon is now faced with his DRAGON LINK team.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Bring our Games to the Heavens
programme.desc: Arion's anti-DRAGON LINK strategy fails, causing more damage to Raimon than the opposing team. Losing confidence and feeling worthless, Arion is ready to surrender when a certain someone suddenly appeals to him.
programme.sub-title: Bring our Games to the Heavens

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Pass to the Future
programme.desc: The battle against DRAGON LINK is over, and the world of football is free once more. Because Raimon's team of skilled players trusted in each other, they restored the ultimate kind of football.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The TV Reporter is here
programme.desc: The fiercely contested Holy Road final is finally over, and the TV cameras have come to Raimon to film a special about Arion and the team who have breathed new life into the game of football.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: This is Raimon Football Club
programme.desc: Continuing on from the previous episode’s look at the current Raimon team, this time we take a look at the history of Raimon’s football club, as told by Coach Evans.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Let’s play soccer!
programme.desc: Mark Evans is the captain of the Raimon Middle School’s long-neglected soccer club. With the club on the verge of being disbanded Mark is hoping to kick it into shape, but he’ll need a little help and more than a little luck.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Royal is here!
programme.desc: Raimon have gotten their first piece of good news, they’re going to play an exhibition game! Except that the game is against the toughest team in the whole country.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Here comes the killer shot!
programme.desc: The team are still on a high from their surprise win against Royal Academy, but there’s a lot of work they still need to do. Kevin is mad at himself and jealous of Axel for scoring the winning shot.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Here comes the Dragon!
programme.desc: It’s game day for Raimon and they’re playing a team that everyone’s nervous about - Occult Jr High.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Where's the notebook?
programme.desc: The Soccer Frontier Tournament is about to start and Raimon are up against the terrifying jumpers of Wild Junior High in their first game. Everyone agrees that unless they come up with a new move, Raimon are finished before they even start.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: This is the Inazuma Drop!
programme.desc: Raimon are all pumped up and ready for their big game against Wild Junior High, all except one player - Jack Wallside. His fear of heights is getting in the way of the Inazuma Drop, and without it all is lost.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Showdown at the riverbank!
programme.desc: Raimon are training hard for the next game in the Soccer Frontier Tournament, and people are beginning to sit up and take notice; including their next opponents - Brainwashing Jr High.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The terrifying soccer cyborgs!
programme.desc: It’s another big game for Raimon, against the robots of Brainwashing Jr High. Nobody’s ever scored a goal against them, much less won, but if Raimon want to advance they have to do just that.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Willy rising!
programme.desc: Axel Blaze is injured and out of Raimon’s next game, but their opponents are the weakest team in the whole tournament, so winning shouldn’t be a problem.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The spy from Royal
programme.desc: Raimon Jr Soccer Club is looking stronger than ever, but so are the forces in league against them.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Find a new coach
programme.desc: The big game against Royal is only a few days away, but unless Raimon Jr can find a new coach then they’re going out without even setting foot on the field!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The finals - Royal Academy - first half!
programme.desc: The boys arrive at Royal Academy for the biggest game of their lives, but before they can begin they have to dispel the cloud of suspicion hanging over the place.
programme.sub-title: The finals - Royal Academy - first half!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Circus Surprise!
programme.desc: Declan has a surprise in store that could swing the duel his way! Can Yuya take down the best the Leo Institute has to offer, or will Declan’s deck prove to be unbeatable?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: The Show Must Go On
programme.desc: Yuya’s down in the dumps, but Principal Boyle’s not having it! Looking to snap Yuya out of his funk, Skip challenges Yuya to a duel to prove that the show must go on!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: In It To Win It
programme.desc: Still stinging from her defeat against the Leo Institute, Zuzu turns to an unlikely source for some assistance – Sora! But before her training can commence, a familiar looking stranger shows up, putting her lesson on hold!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Menu Venue: Part 1
programme.desc: Yuya is served a heaping helping of culinary catastrophe when he duels a celebrity chef with a menu full of merciless food monsters!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Menu Venue: Part 2
programme.desc: The table is set for a frenzied food fight to the finish! Can Yuya handle what Chef Pepper dishes out, or will he lose a lot more than his appetite?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Trapped in a Card
programme.desc: It’s a case of mistaken identity when Yuya is eyed as the primary suspect for attacking Leo students! But when Yuya crosses paths with the real culprit, things go from bad to worse!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Scorching Hot Fight with the Desert Lions!
programme.desc: After Australia, next rivals are here: players used to run and with a lot of stamina. Inazuma National should reinforce those features within the team. Or they should, as soon as they discover why one of them is always leaving training early.
programme.sub-title: The Scorching Hot Fight with the Desert Lions!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Sleeping Tiger Awakes!
programme.desc: Qatar's Desert Lions is putting Inazuma National on a spot. Their stamina and physical game-play is wearing them out little by little. Travis Coach's answer is clear: Austin should dare to give the final step.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Mark vs. Archer!
programme.desc: Archer Hawkins is the strangest of all the members of Inazuma National's team. It looks like as if he had never play football, and still, he's in the team all right.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Possible Substitution?
programme.desc: Inazuma National players have the unexpected visit of Lina Schiller, former Raimon Eleven's coach. She is not coming alone, but with "Neo National"*, a team made from former rivals who didn´t reach the National team.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Coach Travis VS Coach Lina
programme.desc: Neo National Team are set to take Inazuma National place, and its players´ spirit put Inazuma National's in a predicament.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Cammy's Ultimate trick Strategy!
programme.desc: Mark is worried because he needs a new Super-Technique and he cannot come into anything. Cammy is worried over Mark's concern. And Sue will exploit both worries to made up a story that it will lead to the strangest date in history...

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Monkey See, Monkey Duel
programme.desc: When Chazz suddenly goes missing, Jaden and the crew go looking for him, but instead of finding Chazz, they find a dueling monkey who takes one of Alexis's friends hostage!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: A Spirit Summoned
programme.desc: After some students accidentally summon a Duel Monster for real, it's up to Jaden to duel him and win their souls back.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Courting Alexis
programme.desc: Jaden finds himself in an outrageously competitive duel against a sports nut who's bent winning Alexis's heart and making Jaden look bad.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: The Duel Giant
programme.desc: After a menacing Duel Giant is seen around campus, Dr. Crowler convinces Jaden to track him down, but when Jaden catches up with the titan, he must beat him in a duel or become his next victim!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Nature of the Draw
programme.desc: When someone is stealing from the Card Shack, Jaden and the crew go on a stakeout to catch the culprit, but when the thief turns out to be a former student who's been living in the jungle, a truly wild duel ensues.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: The King of Copycats, Part 1
programme.desc: A copycat duelist steals Yugi Muto's deck and mannerisms, and Jaden must duel him to win it back.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Axel's decision
programme.desc: Asian qualifiers´ final is getting near, the whole team is getting ready for this final challenge and new Super-Techniques are being developed to fight their rivals.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The last match
programme.desc: After his father refusal, Axel agrees to drop football as soon as qualifiers are over.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Fire Dragon: the Strongest in Asia!
programme.desc: Finals against Korea seemed a very special game at first glance, and now it's quite more since Inazuma National players finds some old acquaintances in Korean ranks.
programme.sub-title: Fire Dragon: the Strongest in Asia!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Perfect Zone Press
programme.desc: Inazuma is leading the score, but then their rivals start Perfect Zone Press, the strategy which gave them so many victories.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Stand Up Captain!
programme.desc: It's time to took measures to help Inazuma National out of the tight spot they are. While Mark Evans try and think how to do that, Caleb Stonewall.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Let's get our ticket for the world!!
programme.desc: Teams revolution might work, but before that, some players need to be released from the fear and distrust that held them down.
programme.sub-title: Let's get our ticket for the world!!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Playback
programme.desc: Frog and Pigeon plan an exclusive expose on Playmaker after Ghost Gal supplies them with the goods on Link VRAINS’ newest hero!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: An Invitation
programme.desc: Ghost Gal’s gained backdoor access to Sol Tech’s database and Playmaker’s ready to duel her for it!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Camouflaged Chaos
programme.desc: Playmaker hacks into Sol Tech’s database in search of answers, but he finds trouble instead when he runs into a pair of destructive AIs!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Hack Attack
programme.desc: Blue Angel swoops in from the blue to save Playmaker from two AIs designed to destroy!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Blue’s Back!
programme.desc: Blue Angel continues her duel against an AI whose prime directives are: duel, decimate, delete!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Dueling for Answers
programme.desc: Playmaker battles Zaizen to unlock Sol Tech’s databank and the secrets to his past!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Our ticket to the World!
programme.desc: Once they got their pass for Football Frontier International, the team flies to Liocott, the island where the competition will take place.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: This is the World Level!!
programme.desc: The teams taking part have been divided into two groups, and Inazuma National already know who their opponents are.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The English Knights, the Knights of Queen
programme.desc: Knights of Queen will be Inazuma National's first opponent. The game will not be not easy at all, since the "English knights" have quite more football experience and tradition.
programme.sub-title: The English Knights, the Knights of Queen

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: It's Done! My Signature Move!
programme.desc: The match is as tough as it seemed from the very beginning: Knights of Queen's techniques are hurting Inazuma National bad. Specially when Mark cannot stop their shots with his old techniques.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Going Beyond Mugen the Hand!
programme.desc: Tournament does not give a chance to breathe. As soon a game is over, they have to start training for the next.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Curse of Royal, Part 1!
programme.desc: While Darren keeps on looking for a Super-Technique of his own, other Inazuma National's player think they have seen Ray Dark.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: The Number Hunter, Part 1
programme.desc: Yuma and Astral face their toughest battle ever when they are forced to duel a mysterious individual who hunts Number Cards.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: The Number Hunter, Part 2
programme.desc: As the back-and-forth battle between Yuma and the mysterious Number Hunter continues, Yuma must duel like he’s never dueled before if he wants to save Astral, his Number Cards and his soul!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Liv Og Røre!
programme.desc: Molly og Gil ser hvordan Boblekrem muffinsene lages når de går inn på kjøkkenet til Kokken Stef. Guppiene får sin sjanse når de går ut på banen for å spille Liv Og Røre! Det vil kreve samarbeid å drive kjøkkenbasene og bake gode muffins!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Boble Skrubbing
programme.desc: Det ser ut som alle i Bobleby har blitt forkjølet, til og med Herr Grouper! Men ingen fare, i deres helt egen såpeopera, vil Boble Guppiene bruke sin gode hygiene til å hjelpe Herr Grouper bli bedre!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Politi-konkurransen
programme.desc: Stopp i morsomhetenes navn! Konstabel Miranda lærer Gil og de andre barna hvordan poliotiet har lover for at vi skal være trygge. Kan Boble Guppiene bruke et de har lært for å vinne Æresskiltene som Juniorpolitikonstabler?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Kujente Paraden
programme.desc: Yee-haa! Dusty er den tøffeste kujenta i Kujentaparaden! Og hun viser Molly hvordan hun kan bli en kujente også! men når den lille kalven til Dusty får problemer må Molly bruke alt hun har lært for å redde dagen.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Brannhjelper Gil Til Unnsetning!
programme.desc: Når Gil og Boble Guppie sitter fast i et tre blir de reddet av noen heltmodige brannmenn. Men hva skjer når brannfolkene setter seg fast i treet? Kan Gil og Boble Guppiene redde dagen?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Guppie Flyttefolk!
programme.desc: Når flyttedagen til vennen deres, Skip, ikke går som planlagt, Tar Molly, Gil og resten av Guppie Flyttefolkene saken i egne hender og får ting på plass i det nye hjemmet til Skip!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Den glade, den triste og den gretne
programme.desc: Herr Surfisk dukker opp i Lykkestad og gjør hele byen skikkelig gretne! Kan sheriff Molly hjelpe alle med å takle sine vanskelige følelser?
programme.sub-title: Den glade, den triste og den gretne

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Delfiner er våre venner
programme.desc: Molly og Gil møter Kompis, en babydelfin med havets vennligste fjes! I dag er den første buirsdagen til Buddy, og gruppen hans skal holde selskap for ham! Klarer guppiene å vise ham veien til selskapet?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Flukten fra Vulkanøya!
programme.desc: Skipper Molly og Styrmann Gil er skipbrudne på Vulkanøya, og den er i ferd med å få utbrudd, men deler av båten deres begynner å forsvinne! Kommer de seg av øya i tide?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Kroppens organer
programme.desc: Molly og Oona treffer Ordføreren som trener til Bobletuckys årlige maraton! Men når hun får mageknip må hun på sykehuset for å finne ut av det.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: De mektige, rotate titanene!
programme.desc: Når noen rotete titaner (spilt av Guppiene) lager kaos på geitefarmen til Zooli, Nonny, og Oona, må gjeterne reise til Titanenes hjem for å be dem om å rydde opp etter seg.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Smaks-venner!
programme.desc: Kokkene Molly og Gil kjører med matvogna til Platt-land, og oppdager at Baron von Platt bare lar undersåttene sine få spise platt brød! Æsj! Nå må kokkene finne en måte å få smaken tilbake til kongeriket!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Superbilen!
programme.desc: Tauebiler, brannbiler, iskrembiler det er så mange forskjellige biler! Men bare en kan forvandle seg selv til en robot - Superbilen! Men når Superbilen blir sittende fast i søla, er det opp til Gil og Molly å finne den rette bilen for å dra ham opp.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Ja, Så Sanselig
programme.desc: Å nei! Nonny ødela brillene sine! Når de er ferdigreparert, er Nonny fast bestemt på at han skal hente dem på egen hånd. Men for å gjøre det må han stole på de andre fire sansene sine for å komme frem til brillebutikken før den stenger!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Stedet markert med en X
programme.desc: Ohoi sjøulker! Boble Guppiene drar på sjørøvereventyr! Gil og Molly møter en vennlig pirat med et problem; han finner ikke sjørøverskatten sin! Så, utrustet med sjørøverkart, setter Gil, Molly og Boble Puppy seil for å finne stedet markert med en X!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: De Råflotte Rekene!
programme.desc: Mine damer og herrer, gutter og jenter; det utrolig populære Boble Brødre Sirkuset er i byen og Boble Guppiene blir med på forestillingen! Se klovnen Goby, akrobaten Gil, løvetemmer Oona og se opp for flygende paier!

programme.title: Boble Guppier
programme.desc: En liten "Puppy-saurus" blir valgt til å utfordre den regjerende mesteren, tyrannosaurusen Boom Boom, i Tøff Brøler-konkurransen. Der trengs styrke, fart, og ikke minst pågangsmot!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Ånden i boblen
programme.desc: Når Nonny, Gil og Zooli maner fram en ånd, går ånden med på å gi den som gir henne den mest dyrebare gaven, et ønske. De tror det kanskje er en edelsten, men det viser seg at det er vennskap.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: For lyst for en filmkveld
programme.desc: Hvis Månefolket finner en måte å gjøre det mørkt på lyse dagen på, vil Solfolket gå med på å skru av det store nattlyset sitt så Månefokket kan kose seg med nattfilmen sin.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Kom Med Insektene!
programme.desc: Det er insektsparade og Boble Guppiene marsjerer sammen med maurene og summer med biene! Med så mange forskjellige slags insekter har hver Guppie sin favoritt. Og Gil og Molly blir venner med en helt spesiell edderkopp som heter Charlie.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Tempelet Til Den Forsvunnede Valpen
programme.desc: Boble Puppy forsvinner når han biter i et magisk, urgammelt bein og guppiene må ut på en tur full av feller for å finne hunden sin.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Guppiestil (Del 2)
programme.desc: Guppiene drar på skoletur for å se konserten til popstjernen Stilig, som er kjent for alle de kule stilene sine!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Gledelig Jul Herr Surfisk!
programme.desc: Alle i byen skal samles til den store julefesten. Alle, bortsett fra Herr Surfisk.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Et Finn-tastisk Eventyr, del 1
programme.desc: En gang gikk Gil og Molly opp en bakke for å hente vann. Men når en slem heks, spilt av Wanda Sykes, forvandler Boble Puppy til en frosk, må Molly og Gil få hjelp av noen eventyrfigurer for å snu trolldommen.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Havpatruljen!
programme.desc: Stormfulle Pete seiler rundt i verden, og sprer snø i tropiske områder! Klarer Havpatruljen å stoppe snø-angrepet hans?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Ele-elefanter!
programme.desc: Gil ser etter elefanter! Han blir glad når Boble Guppiene ser Snabellkast, et basketballspill som er spilt av tykkhuder! Men kan Gil hjelpe Espen Elefant, den minste elefanten av dem alle, med å score det avgjørende poenget?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Bobbelbiter
programme.desc: Beveg deg gjennom radene i et supermarked sammen med Boble Guppiene når de handler inn frukt, grønnsaker og den siste esken med Boblesnacks til Boble Puppy!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Tilbake Til Skolebenken
programme.desc: Oona er bekymret for vennen sin Avi! Det er første skoledag og han er nervøs. Boble Guppiene lærer oss at skolen er et flott sted til både å leke, lære og til å finne nye venner!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: God Hårdag!
programme.desc: I dag er det fotodag og Gil må klippe det lange håret sitt. Men i frisørsalongen er det kjempelang kø! Alle skal visst klippe seg i dag! Boble Guppiene hjelper frisøren sånn at alle får en god hårdag og ser fantastiske ut på bildet!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: En Guppies Beste Venn
programme.desc: Boble Puppy er forkjølet! Mens Doktor Martinsen tar godt vare på ham, bruker barna dagen til å tenke på hunder, en guppies beste venn. Men vil Gil sitt kort hjelpe Boble Puppy med å føle seg bedre?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Kongeriket Ren
programme.desc: Skitne Deema har stjålet Molly og Gils såpe og gjort Kongeriket Ren veldig skittent! Molly og Gil må få såpen sin tilbake, og gjøre kongeriket rent!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Historien Om Rødfot
programme.desc: Boble Guppiene skal på telttur! Grip lomelykten din og sitt sammen med dem rundt leirbålet hvor du får høre den skumle fortellingen 'Legenden Om Rødfot'.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: God Morgen Herr Surfisk
programme.desc: Boble Guppiene har vikarlærer, Herr Surfisk. Han ser ikke ut til å like noenting! Boble Guppiene må overtale Herr Surfisk så han forstår at yndligstingene deres er verdt å synge om!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Fest Til Havs!
programme.desc: Opp med ankeret! Det er tid for å se på båter i en fest til havs! Men når en diger isball truer med å synke festskipet, vil guppiene klare å bruke kunnskapene sine om havet for å redde dagen, og festen?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Alison i Eventyrland
programme.desc: Postbud Molly prøver å levere et Vennskapsdagkort til ei som heter Alison, som bor i Eventyrland. Men for å gjøre det må hun komme seg forbi den kortstjelende Røde Dronningen, som har gjort Vennskapsdagen forbudt!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Valpen Og Ringen Del 2
programme.desc: I det magiske landet Bobleland, har den onde Natt Trollmannen tatt den magiske ringen til Solkongen! Noen må redde dagen! Vil Molly og Gil få levert ringen tilbake til Solkongen, eller blir det evig natt i Bobleland?

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Guppiene redder julen!
programme.desc: Molly, Gil, og Boble Puppy finner nissens liste i snøen på julaften. De vil levere den tilbake, men da må de holde den ute av hendene til den julehatende humbugen!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: En Ny Kalv!
programme.desc: Med et 'nøff, nøff' her og et 'møø, møø' der, lærer Boble GUppiene seg en hel masse om dyrene på bondegården....og oppdager samtidig at masse av deres yndlignsmat også kommer fra bondegårdene!

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Et Finn-tastisk Eventyr, del 2
programme.desc: En gang gikk Gil og Molly opp en bakke for å hente vann. Men når en slem heks, spilt av Wanda Sykes, forvandler Boble Puppy til en frosk, må Molly og Gil få hjelp av noen eventyrfigurer for å snu trolldommen.

programme.title: Boble Guppier: Boble-Humle-Maraton
programme.desc: Bzzz! Guppiene lever et bie-liv! Å forvandle nektar til honning er mye jobb som krever en masse samarbeid. Kan barna jobbe sammen for å lage honning til dronningbiens te?
